                    <td>Stressed-area licences need town-hall approval and expire after 5 yrs; <strong>Barcelona ends all licences in 2028</strong></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row">Valencian Community</th>
                    <td>VUT</td>
                    <td>Registre de Turisme</td>
